        <header class="bio-head"><span class="lbl">Short bio · 50 words</span><span class="wc">For panel intros, captions</span></header>
        <div class="bio-body" id="bio-short">Tayyub Yaqoob is a UK-based <b>AI and digital-analytics specialist</b>. He has published <b>35+ technical articles</b> in Cointelegraph and AlphaWire on AI agents, machine learning and blockchain, is quoted as an expert source by CCN, and has completed <b>three chapter reviews</b> for IGI Global. Based in Stirling, UK.</div>
        <footer class="bio-foot"><button class="copy-btn" data-target="bio-short">Copy bio</button></footer>
      </article>

      <article class="bio rv" data-bio="medium">
        <header class="bio-head"><span class="lbl">Medium bio · 100 words</span><span class="wc">For podcast notes, programmes</span></header>
        <div class="bio-body" id="bio-medium">Tayyub Yaqoob is a <b>Senior Digital Analyst at 8 Million Stories</b> in Stirling, UK, where he architects proprietary AI-analytics systems used by 50+ client teams. Cointelegraph describes him as a &ldquo;data scientist and AI engineer specialising in machine learning applications across blockchain and marketing analytics.&rdquo; He has published <b>30+ articles</b> in Cointelegraph and <b>5+ in AlphaWire</b>, is quoted as an <b>expert source by CCN</b>, has completed <b>three chapter reviews</b> for IGI Global, and holds AI/ML credentials from Google, AWS and LinkedIn Learning. He is building LedgerTouch &mdash; an independent analytics platform &mdash; in parallel.</div>
        <footer class="bio-foot"><button class="copy-btn" data-target="bio-medium">Copy bio</button></footer>
      </article>

      <article class="bio rv" data-bio="long">
        <header class="bio-head"><span class="lbl">Long bio · ~200 words</span><span class="wc">For feature pieces, profile copy</span></header>
        <div class="bio-body" id="bio-long">Tayyub Yaqoob is a UK-based <b>data scientist and AI engineer</b> working at the intersection of machine learning, blockchain and digital measurement. He is <b>Senior Digital Analyst at 8 Million Stories</b>, where he has designed eight proprietary analytics systems &mdash; forecasters, sentiment models, anomaly detectors and automated reporting engines &mdash; that 50+ client teams depend on each week. His work focuses on the production engineering behind AI / ML systems rather than the demos, with explicit attention to consent, data quality and reproducibility.<br /><br />He has published <b>30+ articles in Cointelegraph</b> and <b>5+ in AlphaWire</b> on AI agents, generative-AI trading, crypto security, quantum-resistance and regulation. He is cited as an <b>expert source by CCN</b>, has completed <b>three peer-reviewed chapter evaluations</b> for IGI Global (on CBDCs, blockchain consensus for IoT banking, and AI-enabled IoT for FinTech), and is currently building LedgerTouch &mdash; an independent analytics platform &mdash; outside of his agency role. He holds an MSc in Computing Science from the University of Stirling, plus AI / ML credentials from Google, AWS and LinkedIn Learning.</div>
        <footer class="bio-foot"><button class="copy-btn" data-target="bio-long">Copy bio</button></footer>
